KitKat::

She started to wake up. the dart's effects did not hold for long.  
She stumbled to her feet. She looked down in her wolf form and saw 
she had been laying in a puddle of mech fluid. She felt like the pit. 
She was about to turn and walk off when she heard the battle still 
raging.  She growled. "Maximal hurt me, not he dies."  She started 
running towards the scent of Windlord.
